data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER Don't miss your opportunity this property has so much to offer.  Nestled among the trees, you'll enjoy the large, newly fenced in backyard and the covered deck which is perfect for grilling and entertaining. New HVAC and New hardwood floors. Upon entering, there is a large family room to gather and enjoy the fireplace.  The kitchen offers stainless steel appliances, butcher block countertops, hardwood floors and tile. Two master suites.  Upstairs master has newly installed cedar plank ceilings with new master bath and closet. Renovations just completed. There are a few walls not completed with some sheetrock and paint.  Call today for your showing. Buyer to confirm sq. footage.
